Package: Rhtslib
Type: Package
Title: htslib high-throughput sequencing library as an R package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person("Martin", "Morgan", email="mtmorgan@fhcrc.org",
             role=c("cre", "aut")))
Description: This package provides an interface to the 'htslib' C
    library for high-throughput sequence analysis. The package is
    primarily of use to developers of other R packages who wish to
    make use of htslib. Motivation and instructions for use of this
    package are in the vignette, vignette(package="htslib", "htslib")
License: Artistic-2.0 | file LICENSE
LazyLoad: yes
Imports: zlibbioc
LinkingTo: zlibbioc
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: http://www.htslib.org/
biocViews: DataImport,  Sequencing
